column2: # Question 1: Fit this data by Cumulative logit model with ungrouped data with proportional odds
# cumulative probability and the effect of x is identical for all cumulative logits

vglm(formula = Impairment ~ LifeEvents + SES, family = cumulative(parallel = TRUE), 
    data = impairment)
No Hauck-Donner effect found in any of the estimates
# Question 2: Fit this data by Cumulative logit model with ungrouped data with non-proportional odds
# cumulative probability and the effect of x is identical for all cumulative logits

vglm(formula = Impairment ~ LifeEvents + SES, family = cumulative(parallel = FALSE), 
    data = impairment)
Warning: Hauck-Donner effect detected in the
